{"tid":2445300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳紐政府聯合聲明　斥人大改選舉制度毀香港自治","createTime":"2021-03-13T13:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T21:06:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2f52825de5e1f4fec5c312bec66e96002e65aa","tid":2445300,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:44:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%96%B9%E5%89%B2%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E6%BE%B3%E7%B4%90%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E6%96%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%94%B9%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E6%AF%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2596%25B9%25E5%2589%25B2%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25B4%2590%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=2eef4520\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2596%25B9%25E5%2589%25B2%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25B4%2590%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F&h=d64c043d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%96%B9%E5%89%B2%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E6%BE%B3%E7%B4%90%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E6%96%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%94%B9%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E6%AF%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB/</a><br />\n<br />\n北京出手大幅修改香港選舉制度，封殺民主派參選。繼七大工業國（G7）外長昨（12 日）發表聯合聲明後(詳見報道)，澳洲及新西蘭政府今（13 日）亦發聯合聲明，指對人大通過改變香港選舉制度深表關注，認為此舉破壞《中英聯合聲明》中，讓香港可享有高度自治、權利及自由直到 2047 年的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中又指這些改變與以普選產生行政長官的終極目標背道而馳，甚至削弱香港的民主體制、損害《基本法》賦予的言論及結社自由。這重大改變必定會收窄香港的自治權。澳洲與新西蘭政府促請香港和中央恪守承諾，讓港人擁有真正參與管治的渠道，同時保護立法會作為各方意見表達平台和監察政府的角色。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署：西方國家險惡、卑鄙 把香港作棋子遏制中國發展<br />\n<br />\n另外，外交部駐港特派員公署今（13 日）亦發聲明，表明對「少數西方國家單獨或聯合發表所謂聲明」，詆毀人大就完善香港選舉制度的決定，是「粗暴踐踏國際法和國際關係基本準則」，形容是「赤裸裸」干預香港事務和中國內政，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，「任何干預香港事務的行徑都是痴心妄想」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中又指，少數西方國家打著「民主」、「自由」的幌子，對香港事務指手劃腳，「所謂聲明、報告」違背基本事實，實質是「包庇縱容反中亂港份子」，「暴露他們把香港當作棋子遏制中國發展的險惡用心和卑鄙伎倆」。"},{"pid":"fae9fc76ab82179eae1dc1a40da2acd024b35dc8","tid":2445300,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.foreignminister.gov.au/minister/marise-payne/media-release/joint-statement-electoral-changes-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignminister.gov.au%2Fminister%2Fmarise-payne%2Fmedia-release%2Fjoint-statement-electoral-changes-hong-kong&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=a762adf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foreignminister.gov.au/minister/marise-payne/media-release/joint-statement-electoral-changes-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n聲明原文"},{"pid":"3b5287f0047ca959dcef2b82199f9d940eb266f0","tid":2445300,"uid":55955,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"中共一早預咗成堆國家會出聲明反對<br />\n但係wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出聲明又唔痛"},{"pid":"3d49a08afd0452a1eae7523e5e6e67b0a1047aaf","tid":2445300,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3b5287f0047ca959dcef2b82199f9d940eb266f0","tid":2445300,"uid":55955,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"中共一早預咗成堆國家會出聲明反對<br />\n但係wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出聲明又唔痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:4